#: src/uagent/core.py:969
msgid ""
"- Summarize the conversation log so far in English.\n"
"- Keep the summary concise but include key decisions, constraints, and pending items.\n"
"- Output should be directly usable as a system message titled 'Summary of the conversation so far'.\n"
msgstr ""
"- これまでの会話ログを英語で要約してください。\n"
"- 簡潔にしつつ、主要な決定事項、制約、保留中の項目を含めてください。\n"
"- 出力は 'Summary of the conversation so far' というタイトルの system メッセージとして、そのまま使える形にしてください。\n"

#: src/uagent/core.py:1042
#, fuzzy, python-format
msgid "429 retry limit (%(max_retries)s) reached while history compression."
msgstr "429 Retry limit (%(max_retries)s) reached."

#: src/uagent/core.py:1052
#, python-format
msgid "Error while calling LLM for history compression: %(err)r"
msgstr "レスポンス解析中にエラー: %(err)r"

#: src/uagent/core.py:1070
msgid "Summary of the conversation so far:\n"
msgstr "これまでの会話の要約:\n"

#: src/uagent/core.py:1078
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"[INFO] Conversation history was summarized by the LLM: old_part={old_n} -> 1"
